## ğŸ“š Key Takeaways

âœ… **Gatekeeper enforces standards** before deployments reach runtime environments

âœ… **Monitor mode** allows deployments but sends notifications (non-blocking)

âœ… **Protect mode** blocks deployments that fail gates (blocking)

âœ… **All failures** generate email notifications with remediation guidance

âœ… **Start with Monitor** to gather data, then switch to Protect for enforcement

âœ… **Use for critical checks** like security, compliance, and quality gates

